# Walkthrough - Stability Fixes & Bug Resolutions

I have implemented a series of fixes to address the game crashes and improve overall application stability.

## Fixes Implemented

### 1. Navigation Stability
- **[main.dart](file:///Users/amolsehgal/antigravity%20-%20touchline%20tantrum/touchline_tantrum/lib/main.dart)**: Defined the `/game` named route. This prevents the "Undefined Route" crash that occurred when clicking "RESUME CAREER".

### 2. Async Safety & Resource Management
- **[game_screen.dart](file:///Users/amolsehgal/antigravity%20-%20touchline%20tantrum/touchline_tantrum/lib/screens/game_screen.dart)**: 
    - Added `if (!mounted) return;` checks to all [Timer](file:///Users/amolsehgal/antigravity%20-%20touchline%20tantrum/touchline_tantrum/lib/screens/game_screen.dart#211-227) and `Future` callbacks calling `setState`. This prevents "setState() called after dispose()" crashes.
    - Optimized `SharedPreferences` by caching the instance during initialization, reducing I/O overhead.
    - Removed redundant `AudioPlayer` instance to conserve memory.

### 3. UI Optimization
- **[breaking_news_ticker.dart](file:///Users/amolsehgal/antigravity%20-%20touchline%20tantrum/touchline_tantrum/lib/widgets/breaking_news_ticker.dart)**:
    - Reduced animation frequency from 50ms to 100ms.
    - Cached the joined news string to avoid expensive processing during every build cycle.
    - Added `mounted` checks for the scroll timer.

### 4. Logic & Integration Fixes
- **[manager_mood.dart](file:///Users/amolsehgal/antigravity%20-%20touchline%20tantrum/touchline_tantrum/lib/widgets/manager_mood.dart)**: Fixed a threshold bug where it was checking for values > 30 instead of > 0.3 (normalized percentages).
- **[game_screen.dart](file:///Users/amolsehgal/antigravity%20-%20touchline%20tantrum/touchline_tantrum/lib/screens/game_screen.dart)**: Fully integrated the [ManagerMood](file:///Users/amolsehgal/antigravity%20-%20touchline%20tantrum/touchline_tantrum/lib/widgets/manager_mood.dart#3-61) widget into the game UI.
- **[audio_manager.dart](file:///Users/amolsehgal/antigravity%20-%20touchline%20tantrum/touchline_tantrum/lib/utils/audio_manager.dart)**: Added 2-second timeouts and improved error logging for network-based sounds to prevent app hangs on poor connections.

## Verification Results

- **`flutter analyze`**: Passed with zero errors or warnings (only info-level deprecation notes remain).
- **Navigation**: "RESUME CAREER" now correctly navigates to the game screen without crashing.
- **Resource Cleanup**: Timers now stop correctly when navigating away from screens.
